 to the Committee, that some of the basic admin jobs carried out in Abercrombie House have just been absorbed into higher</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">&#x2011;</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">grade specifications, which means that we have people being paid big sums of money and who are meant to be delivering programmes—the jobs they have been recruited to—and their time is being spent on basic admin duties</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">If that detail could be supplied, I would be grateful</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Chair:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> That could be in writing.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:34pt"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold">Q70</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Mr McCann:</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> Writing is fine, yes</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">The question that I have is this</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">I know you have not given us a formal response to the </span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">Scotland</span><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt"> report, but I personally was very concerned about a lac